Interface BugPatternMatcher<T extends com.sun.source.tree.Tree>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - the expression Tree

    @Internal
public interface BugPatternMatcher<T extends com.sun.source.tree.Tree>
    A basic interface to match the given expression against some known case of the BugPattern.

    • Method Detail

      • matches

        boolean matches(T tree,
                com.google.errorprone.VisitorState state)
        Checks if the given expression matches the BugPattern case processed by this class.

        The method should be used from inside the BugChecker implementations, so the Error Prone scanners provide the proper Tree and VisitorState corresponding to the currently assessed expression.

        Parameters:
        tree - the expression Tree
        state - the current VisitorState
        Returns:
        true if the expression matches the bug pattern and false otherwise

        Fixes for the processed bug pattern case
